subject: College Athletics
Hockey, Ice
lead_paragraph: Jinelle Zaugg scored twice and Jessie Vetter made 33 saves to help the two-time defending champion Wisconsin beat Harvard, 4-1, on Thursday in the N.C.A.A. women’s Frozen Four semifinals.
